      <p class="text-gray-700 text-lg mb-4">
        <strong>Mixo for beginners.</strong> Easiest way to get online at best price.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-700 text-lg mb-4">
        <strong>Webflow for power users.</strong> If you need maximum control and are willing to learn.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        Choose Mixo for simplicity and value. Choose Webflow for power and flexibility.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <div class="text-center">
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-8">Mixo for ease and value. Webflow for power and flexibility. Different tools for different needs.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/reviews/mixo-ai" class="bg-orange-600 hover:bg-orange-700 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold text-lg">
          Read Mixo Review â†’
        </a>
        <a href="/reviews/webflow-ai" class="bg-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-800 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold text-lg">
          Read Webflow Review â†’
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- FAQ SECTION -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 border-t border-gray-200">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-8">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="border-l-4 border-sky-500 pl-6">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">Is Mixo or Webflow better for website building?</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Both Mixo and Webflow score 8.5/10 overall but serve completely different purposes. Mixo offers much better ease of use (9.0/10 vs 7.0/10), faster setup (9.0/10 vs 7.5/10), superior value for money (9.0/10 vs 7.5/10), and significantly more affordable pricing at $9/month vs $15/month. Webflow offers superior design quality (9.0/10 vs 8.0/10), much better flexibility (9.5/10 vs 8.0/10), powerful CMS capabilities (9.5/10), and code export capability that Mixo lacks. Mixo is better for: beginners, bloggers, portfolios, simple business sites, users wanting maximum value and ease. Webflow is better for: designers, agencies, complex content sites, power users wanting complete control.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="border-l-4 border-sky-500 pl-6">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">What is the price difference between Mixo and Webflow?</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Mixo and Webflow have different pricing structures with Mixo being more affordable at entry levels. Mixo starts at $9/month for all features, $19/month for premium plans, up to $39/month for advanced features. Over 3 years, Mixo costs $324-1404 depending on plan level. Webflow starts at $15/month for basic sites, $29/month for CMS features, up to $59/month for advanced plans. Over 3 years, Webflow costs $540-2124 depending on plan level. For basic websites, Mixo is more affordable ($9 vs $15/month base pricing). For CMS features, the gap widens ($19 vs $29/month). Mixo's aggressive pricing makes it exceptional value for budget-conscious users who don't need Webflow's power.</p>
